ication Table Entry|region=Sweden|certyear=2014|relyear=2013|artist=Jason Derulo|title=Trumpets|award=Gold|type=single|certref=<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.sverigetopplistan.se/netdata/ghl002.mbr/artdata?dfom=20140101&sart=3569513 | title=Jason Derulo \u2013 Trumpets | publisher=[[Swedish Recording Industry Association|Grammofon Leverant\u00f6rernas F\u00f6rening]] | access-date=October 2, 2014 | language=sv}}</ref>}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=United Kingdom|type=single|artist=Jason Derulo|title=Trumpets|access-date=February 2, 2014|relyear =2013|certyear=2014|award=Platinum}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=United States|type=single|artist=Jason Derulo|title=Trumpets|access-date=February 2, 2014|relyear =2013|certyear=2015|award=Platinum|number=2}}\n!scope=\"col\" colspan=\"3\"| Streaming\n|-\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Denmark|certyear=2014|relyear=2014|artist=Jason Derulo|title=Trumpets|award=Platinum|number=2|certref=<ref>{{cite web|access-date= October 2, 2014 |title= Certificeringer \u2013 Jason Derulo \u2013 Trumpets|url= http://www.ifpi.dk/?q=content/jason-derulo-trumpets-1 |publisher= [[IFPI Denmark]]}}</ref>|type=single|certmonth=8|salesamount=5,200,000}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Spain|certyear=2015|relyear=2014|artist=David Guetta feat. Sam Martin|title=Dangerous|award=Platinum|certref=<ref>{{cite web|access-date= January 10, 2015|title= Canciones - 29-12-2014 a 4-1-2015|url= http://www.promusicae.es/listas/semana/2777-canciones-semana-1-2015 |publisher= [[PROMUSICAE]]|format = PDF|language = Spanish}}</ref>|type=single|certmonth=1|salesamount=10,000,000}}\n{{Certification Table Bottom|streaming=true}}\n\n==Credits and personnel==\nCredits adapted from the liner notes for ''Tattoos''.<ref name=\"album credits\" />\n* [[Vocals]]&nbsp;\u2013 [[Jason Derulo]]\n* [[Lyrics]]&nbsp;\u2013 [[Jason Derulo|Jason Desrouleaux]], [[Jon Bellion]]\n* [[Record producer|Producer]]&nbsp;\u2013 [[Jon Bellion]]\n* [[Sound recording and reproduction Recorded]] By&nbsp;\u2013 Vince Watson at [[Atlantic Recording Studios]], Hollywood, CA\n* Additional Recordings&nbsp;\u2013 Josh Collins and Juan P. Negrete\n* [[Audio mixing (recorded music)|Mixed]] by&nbsp;\u2013 Roberto \"Tito\" Vazquez at Plush Recording Studios, Orlando FL\n* [[Audio mastering|Mastered]] by&nbsp;\u2013 Tom Coyne at Sterling Sound in New York.\n* [[Record label|Label]]&nbsp;\u2013 [[Warner Bros. Records]] Inc.\n\n== Release history ==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\"\n|-\n! scope=\"column\"| Region !! Date !! Format !! Label\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| United Kingdom\n|| November 7, 2013\n|| [[Urban contemporary]]\n| rowspan=\"4\"| {{flatlist|\n* [[Warner Music Group]]\n* [[Beluga Heights]]\n}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Australia<ref>{{cite web|author=Steffen Hung |url=http://australian-charts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Jason+Derulo&titel=Trumpets |title=Jason Derulo \u2013 Trumpets |publisher=australian-charts.com |date= |accessdate=2014-02-22}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"2\"| December 2, 2013\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[Top 40 radio]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | New Zealand<ref>{{cite web|author=Steffen Hung |url=https://charts.nz/showitem.asp?interpret=Jason+Derulo&titel=Trumpets |title=Jason Derulo \u2013 Trumpets |publisher=charts.nz |date= |accessdate=2014-02-22}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| United States\n|| August 21, 2014\n|| [[Top 40 radio|Mainstream Top 40]]\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n{{Jason Derulo}}\n\n[[Category:2013 singles]]\n[[Category:Jason Derulo songs]]\n[[Category:Music videos directed by Colin Tilley]]\n[[Category:Pop ballads]]\n[[Category:UK R&B Singles Chart number-one singles]]\n[[Category:Songs about sexuality]]\n[[Category:Songs written by Jon Bellion]]\n[[Category:Songs written by Jason Derulo]]\n", "name_user": "John of Reading", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eMusic video:Typo fixing, replaced: songs release \u2192 song's release", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Trumpets_(Jason_Derulo_so